{"tid":85442,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"喂呀，黃洋達你唔好咁大愛劉德華得唔得呀","createTime":"2017-01-18T10:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T13:12:52.000Z","uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6382f88b815dd9ac3780c78dac2e2b312ebfea03","tid":85442,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g149q0d3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg149q0d3&h=232eeb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉德華港豬黎啵<br />\n<br />\n冇支持過你永續基本法架，佢幫道地賣廣告炸，唔係幫你永續難本法架<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多上左年紀既廢老廢中好鐘意佢架<br />\n<br />\n即係何cc 黃耀明 唱雨傘主題曲就落地獄，從來唔講政治野既明星就得到祝福<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得有人話做熱狗朋友不如做泛民朋友，而做泛民朋友又不如做港豬，做港豬又不如做保皇啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，當初你地話退出抗爭專心社區工作。 高登同facebook一堆人話 「好！！香港人唔投熱普城應得此報」<br />\n<br />\n香港人依家係你地公敵黎架，你黃洋達咁樣係熱血政治不正確。"},{"pid":"ae56da2afb5f5aca774ebe7050537f294fdeda67","tid":85442,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:30:43.000Z","msg":"虛偽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c921eb0fcef97005ae6f48f4c21e694c7b4b17e9","tid":85442,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>虛偽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢想永瀆基本法推華仔做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213c0527ab052d39f99799263527cf97993a8388","tid":85442,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fe06ea218f5900f3a0273e1a1ec85d885c1ce68","tid":85442,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"303b5f02bdd2ce7ec3365ccb82e16919a079009a","tid":85442,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}